{"tid":341927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨　早有後著　高鐵通車後　日失8000萬元　可由政府付錢","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T10:52:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"234d38371c026d5de936c46556dabe6cf7708b07","tid":341927,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1586817&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1586817%26target%3D2&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=c004a108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1586817%26target%3D2&h=80a5f436\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1586817&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/04/23/116733/i_510x340_930603123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F116733%2Fi_510x340_930603123.jpg&h=35ccb242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　本報早前獨家報道，港鐵須在今年七、八月獲批高鐵營運管理權，始能讓高鐵香港段如期在明年第三季通車。港鐵主席馬時亨昨接受電台訪問時承認，正與政府當局接觸商討高鐵營運事宜，尚未達落實階段，期望能於今年七月新政府上任時與港府簽署合約。<br />\n<br />\n　　他解釋，營運高鐵牽涉的人手預計過千人，港鐵需時招聘及訓練，他明白政府面對不少掣肘，包括處理一地兩檢等，仍期望能盡早處理營運權問題。他又傾向由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港鐵向政府收取定額營運費</strong></span>，「只收回成本，另加少許費用」，認為較分帳模式簡單，能較快與政府達成共識，但尚未計算實際數目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170423/s00001/1492884259689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170423%2Fs00001%2F1492884259689&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=93d840cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170423%2Fs00001%2F1492884259689&h=0ca61638\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170423/s00001/1492884259689</a><br />\n<br />\n田北辰：定額減改善服務誘因<br />\n<br />\n如港鐵向港府收取定額營運費，將不受高鐵賺蝕影響，立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰認為對高鐵運作未必有利，擔心港鐵無誘因做好服務，變相令政府承擔所有風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155471953792357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155471953792357&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=209960c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155471953792357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n問: 高鐵使用率低怎辦?<br />\n答: 加港鐵價錢填數就可以了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁偉堯: 港鐵冇咁笨！馬屎坑講過話想收經營服務費！"},{"pid":"ba457e4920295122d1b800f66d2bbbe337502495","tid":341927,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"好高經濟效益呀我屌你老母"},{"pid":"01bf629812e52b546de95522278aedbbbe685c79","tid":341927,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5db3d5f1e265ee75c0bcef62544876b0d534b2","tid":341927,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"要填氹不如停撚左佢"},{"pid":"77e9d10bda412e73857abbebcba231870e229016","tid":341927,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"學邊個邊個講不如炸撚左去啦"}]}